Package: mumosa
Type: Package
Authors@R: person("Aaron", "Lun", role = c("aut", "cre"), email="infinite.monkeys.with.keyboards@gmail.com")
Version: 0.99.0
Date: 2020-11-09
License: GPL-3
Title: Multi-Modal Single-Cell Analysis Methods
Description: 
    Assorted utilities for multi-modal analyses of single-cell datasets.
    Includes functions to combine multiple modes for downstream analysis,
    combine alternative experiments into a single object for visualization, 
    and to compute correlations between assay values for different modes.
Depends: 
    SingleCellExperiment
